description: In this TWO PART SERIES, Evangelist Knott takes an in-depth look at the parable of the LOST COIN from two perspectives - the PERSONAL and the PROPHETIC. As you listen, may you come to a better understanding of God's will for you as an individual and for His people as a whole. This sermon will prove to be a blessing to you, your family and friends.
